          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/40630514/" class=" " title="kelly">kelly</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24587109">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">善或许得不到回报，但可以找到安慰。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-15 16:05</span>
                  
