              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26016108/" class="">第9页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cayixxxxx/" class=" " title="啦啦啦啦啦啦啦">啦啦啦啦啦啦啦</a>
                (想说，天空很蓝。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26016108">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">黑乎乎的土地似乎有着各种各样的颜色，以花草的形式表现出来。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-26 16:15</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
